  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        The study population will consist of patients with chronic hepatitis C mono-or co-infected
        with HIV.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients 18 years of age.

          -  Patients with expected prison stay beyond the duration of follow-up period of the
             study.

          -  Patients with chronic HCV infection and detectable viral load to initiate treatment
             with standard therapy.

          -  Patients their written informed consent to participate in the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients previously treated with Interferon (IFN) and Ribavirin (RBV).

          -  Patients can not read or understand a written questionnaire at the discretion of the
             investigator.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
